# 🌤️ Weather App

A responsive weather application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript using the OpenWeather API.

## Features

- 🔍 Search weather by city
- 🌡️ Current temperature
- 🌥️ Weather condition
- 💧 Humidity
- 💨 Wind speed
- 📅 Current date
- 📈 5-day forecast
- ❌ Invalid city handling
- 📱 Responsive design

## Technologies

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- Fetch API
- OpenWeather API

